---
title: Cheesy Beef Burger & Kumara Wedges with Caramelised Onion & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Tomato sauce is always classic on a burger, but this time we’ve swapped it out for two of our other favourite classics; creamy pesto dressing and caramelised onion. Served with baked kumara wedges, you’ll be thanking us all night for this easy and mouth-watering meal.
